IMHO this is related to this issue:
perfsonar/mesh-config/issues/113

When the API pulls JSON out, it replaces any name that has "_" as a prefix with null. As a result, all values with such names that are being taken from the command line and converted to the JSON spec will be changed to null and will not conform to the type associated with that value. 
